    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 997.1 Carrera S, featuring the 3.8L M97.01 flat-six powerplant. This example boasts a pristine bore-scope report and a factory-spec 6-speed manual transmission with a crisp, short-throw linkage. The PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) remains perfectly calibrated, providing exceptional damping control. Finished in a concours-level exterior, the undercarriage reflects a dry-climate history with zero oxidation on the suspension components. The N-rated Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires wrap staggered Carrera Sport wheels, ensuring maximum lateral grip. Mechanically stock with a documented service history, this is a turn-key collector-grade driver.",
