    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and hand-washed since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory aroma, with the premium hand-stitched leather seating showing no bolster wear, creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation and climate controls, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at the original dealership on a time-based schedule rather than mileage, and I have a comprehensive binder of every service receipt and inspection report. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, the transmission shifts with silk-like smoothness, and the premium tires have less than 500 miles of wear. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
